Package com.shouldis.bitset.parallel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayBiterator
    Implementation of SizedBiterator used to stream all values within a specified integer array representing indices in an order appropriate to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    Biterator
    Implementation of Spliterator that is meant to be used in conjunction with BitSets.
    DeadBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator used to stream the indices of dead bits within a BitSet, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    LiveBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator used to stream the indices of live bits within a BitSet, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    RangeBiterator
    Implementation of SizedBiterator used to stream all indices of a specified range, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    SizedBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator that is meant to be used when streaming a known number of indices.
